  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h3><strong>Explore the lakes and mountains of Europe with an Inghams family holiday. Our dedicated team of holiday experts have hand-picked the best destinations for your next family adventure.</strong></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13067868/inghams-lakes-and-mountains-family-summer-holidays-eating-picnic.jpg" alt="Family enjoying a picnic in the Lakes &amp; Mountains" data-udi="umb://media/fb5c0a331c1f4bb9a6d5c42768d7ea1d" /></p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Active Family Holidays in Europe</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We offer fantastic and unforgettable family holidays in the most beautiful destinations across Europe. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Each of our family-friendly resorts offer varied sports and activity programmes, as well as naturally beautiful and spacious surroundings in the Lakes and Mountains of Europe, ideal for active days out. We want your family holiday to be special, memorable, and the perfect mix of fun and relaxation.</span></p>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<div> </div>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Why book a family activity holiday with Inghams?</h2>
</div>
<div>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Huge range of activities</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090580/italy-lake-family-board-walk314x193.jpg" alt="Summer family holiday Europe" data-udi="umb://media/9e293f511adc405ba219e42c63f8a0f7" /></p>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">You can choose from a range of family holiday destinations and activities to suit your family’s needs. Whether you prefer the excitement of water sports, the new challenges of mountain biking or exploring at your own pace on foot, you’ll have endless fun on an Inghams family holiday.</span></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3> Kid activity clubs </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090581/kids-tennis-314x193.jpg" alt="Kids clubs active family holiday" data-udi="umb://media/ff12e355dcfa412e950875452f1cc6bc" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We’ve made it as easy for you to find the perfect activities to keep your mini explorers entertained. Many of our resorts and selected hotels offer activity clubs so whether you want to relax or take a day out to explore, you’ll have peace of mind knowing your kids are in safe hands.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>We make it easy</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089976/amalfi-coast-314x193.jpg" alt="Amalfi Coast" data-udi="umb://media/9ec30b529208452ab62dd884a16a0c63" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We take care of everything so you don’t have to. With flights, hotel and transfers included, as well as a range of in-resort offers and discounts, you can enjoy all the excitement of your chosen destination, without worrying about any of the little details.</span></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Family Holiday Destinations</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We’ve handpicked the best resorts in Europe for family activity holidays. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Whether you want to hike through the mountains, explore the countryside, or enjoy a fun water sports activity, there’s something for everyone.</span></p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Family holidays to Italy</strong></h3>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Lake Garda, Italy </h2>
<p><img src="/media/13090573/lake-garda-408x200.jpg" alt="Lake Garda family holiday" data-udi="umb://media/2098412b61f4489484436ad4336e18a9" /></p>
<p><span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Every day is an adventure in Lake Garda. This resort offers endless opportunities for outdoor fun, sightseeing and exploring. It is home to Italy’s largest theme parks, striking medieval castles and child-friendly museums. Whether you want to explore these activities, or simply relax by the lakeside, the choice is yours. </span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Gardaland Park</strong> - Chase some thrills at Italy's top amusement park.</span></span></li>
<li><span><strong>Walking &amp; Cycling</strong> - There are plenty of trails for all abilities, from gentle strolling to uphill mountain paths.</span><span></span></li>
<li><span><strong>Exciting Watersports</strong> - Try your hand at windsurfing, kitesurfing and paddle boarding.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Family holidays in Lake Garda">Find out more about Lake Garda &gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Canazei - Dolomites, Italy </h2>
<p><img src="/media/13090575/dolomites-walkers-400x208.jpg" alt="Dolomites family holiday" data-udi="umb://media/034ae147ce1b421d8f47031b74a1c02b" /></p>
<p><span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Escape into the mountains and immerse yourself in the Dolomites landscape. This family-friendly resort offers a wide range of activities that cater for every ability. Discover hidden walking trails, take an exhilarating bike ride, or brush up on your history knowledge at the Great War Museum - there’s plenty to do and see.</span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Doloandes Wellness Centre</strong> - Whether you’re splashing about in the pools or taking some time out in the relaxing areas, it’s the perfect place to unwind.</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Dolomiti Action Adventure Park</strong> - Test your courage, skill and sense of balance with ziplining,  balance beans and suspended rope bridges.</span></li>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Cycling</strong> -  Take a break in nature and explore the beautiful landscape. There are over 400 cycling routes to explore so you’re sure to find one that suits you.</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/7075240655bf40a19a9c77b24d8c5082" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7075240655bf40a19a9c77b24d8c5082}" title="Canazei">Find out more about Canazei &gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Family holidays to Austria</strong></h3>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Mayrhofen - Austria</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13090576/maryhofen-birds-show-400x208.jpg" alt="Mayrhofen Family Holiday" data-udi="umb://media/d9b5c05a3b9841d19a270c2f97c1c2b3" /></p>
<p><span><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re looking for a summer playground where you’ll never get bored, the Mayrhofen is the resort that will keep on giving. Surrounded by beautiful mountains, alpine wildlife and exhilarating activities, it’s not hard to see why it is one of Europe’s top family mountain resorts.</span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Bird of prey show</strong> - The Ahorn mountain has a lovely loop walk, with a daily birds of prey show and barbeque area.</span></span></li>
<li><span><strong>Natural water playground <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.zillertal.at/en/suche/poi/detail/430013234/wassernaturspielplatz-brindlang.html" target="_blank">‘Brindlang</a></strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>’</strong> - This adventure playground can be found at the heart of Scheuling Forest.</span></span></li>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong><a rel="noopener" href="https://kristallwelten.swarovski.com/Content.Node/wattens/Visitor_information.en.html" target="_blank">Swarovski Crystal World</a></strong> -  Highlights include the Chambers of Wonder, the Crystal Cloud, the Playtower and Playground.</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Family Holiday in  Mayrhofen">Find out more about Mayrhofen &gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Zell am See, Austria </h2>
<p><img src="/media/13090578/zel-am-see-lake-408x200.jpg" alt="Zell am See family holiday" data-udi="umb://media/bd77be43ea764cdcb2556dce543d123d" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For nature lovers looking for a summer holiday spot, this family-friendly mountain lake resort is the perfect destination. The town sits on the shore of the crystal-clear Lake Zell, surrounded by majestic mountains, and is full of fun activities. </span></p>
<ul>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Watersports on the lake</strong> - There are three lidos in Zell am See which offer a childrens pool, adventure pool, swimming floats, slides and diving.</span></span></li>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Weekly organised kid activities</strong> - For children 5-15 years. Activities include a day on the farm, a pirate day on the shores of Lake Zell, archery and more.</span></span></li>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>The Schmidolin, the cool dragon</strong> - The whole family will love the action, fun and games on the Schmittenhohe mountain.</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/2631ac5f3f824554a6f8c73491b2efae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2631ac5f3f824554a6f8c73491b2efae}" title="Zell am See">Find out more about Zell am See &gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Chamonix, France </h2>
<p><img src="/media/13090579/chamonix-family-walking-408x200.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/797abf51a1ec491791770418824dccfa" /></p>
<p><span><span style="font-weight: 400;">There are plenty of outdoor activities in this resort, such as rafting, parapenting, mountain biking, climbing, horse riding, and summer tobogganing. It doesn't matter what you're into, Chamonix has something for everyone.</span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span><a rel="noopener" href="http://www.parcdemerlet.com/en/" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Merlet Animal Park</strong></span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> - Children will love exploring this animal park, where eight species of alpine wildlife roam freely in a cleared section of the mountain side.</span></span></li>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>The farmers market</strong> - It takes place in Mont Blanc Square every Saturday morning, with lots of food stands featuring local cheese, fruit and veg.</span></span></li>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Walking routes for all ages</strong> - From relaxing strolls to challenging hikes, there’s walking routes that the whole family can enjoy. </span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Find out more about Chamonix &gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Saas Fee, Switzerland</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13090577/saas-fee-toboggan-408x200.jpg" alt="Saas Fee family holiday summer" data-udi="umb://media/d02aa613a65f4f1a860e2966bb5f651a" /></p>
<p><span><span style="font-weight: 400;">The whole family will enjoy the activities in Saas Fee. Whether you're exploring the local terrain, feeding the local wildlife, or satisfying your inner climber at the local rope park, there are countless adventures to be had.</span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.saas-fee.ch/en/familie/summer/family-activities-in-summer/feeblitz-toboggan-run" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Tobogganing</strong></span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> - Take the steepest toboggan lift in the Alps up to the start of the track, then hurtle back down the mountain! Lots of fun for all the family.</span></span></li>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Adventure activities</strong> - Lots of activities including an adventure forest, children's playground, monster scooters and themed walking trails.</span></span></li>
<li><span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Golf course</strong> -  Enjoy a round of</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> golf at this alpine range. There’s also mini-golf for the beginners in the family.</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e}" title="Saas Fee">Find out more about Saas Fee &gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Our top recommended family hotels </h2>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/dbb6092a157a4b7eaca7525ba4ab65ac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dbb6092a157a4b7eaca7525ba4ab65ac}" title="Parc Hotel"><strong>Parc Hotel - 4 Stars</strong></a></p>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img src="/media/13090557/parc-hotel-peschiera-260x141.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/f360cd7f08124a12bdf2607618f928ff" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/0f9f33f516a448a2ab8bda68f2fba594" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0f9f33f516a448a2ab8bda68f2fba594}" title="Peschiera"><strong>Peschiera, Lake Garda</strong></a></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This hotel is an excellent choice for families. There are plenty of activities on offer, including swimming pools, a sports centre, mini-golf course and skate park. With a buzzing holiday club atmosphere, there will always be something to keep the whole family entertained.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a9ffe05a6c554c56b0932e764beba1da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a9ffe05a6c554c56b0932e764beba1da}" title="Hotel Iseolago"><strong>Hotel Iseolago - 4 Stars</strong></a></p>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img style="width: 260px; height: 141px;" src="/media/13090558/hotel-iseolago-pool-lake-iseo-260x141.jpg?width=260&amp;height=141" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7b3cb7ad37b64a5ea801931162862d36" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9}" title="Lake Iseo"><strong>Lake Iseo</strong></a></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This family-friendly hotel is surrounded by beautiful gardens for little ones to run around in. It has three pools to choose from, including one for younger children. It’s also only one kilometre from Lake Iseo, with a private pathway leading from the hotel grounds.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/0b016888041749faa50b77ee5e28380a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0b016888041749faa50b77ee5e28380a}" title="Residence Villa Maria">Residence Villa Maria - 4 Stars</a></strong></p>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img style="width: 260px; height: 141px;" src="/media/13090559/residenice-villa-maria-italy-260x141.jpg?width=260&amp;height=141" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7dd3c3817ba140af8e8b1d6e88ad84ca" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/574a76e62f8b4388af2fd61b34c7ed1b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/574a76e62f8b4388af2fd61b34c7ed1b}" title="Desenzano"><strong>Desenzano, Lake Garda</strong></a></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">These self catering apartments are perfect for families. They are located in a peaceful park area, just outside Desenzano. There’s plenty to keep you and the children entertained, with a swimming pool, tennis court and bikes to hire - a fun way to explore the area!</span></p>
<div class="g4"></div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/13d40418b4da40d795c1847c52c88cea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/13d40418b4da40d795c1847c52c88cea}" title="Neuhaus Zillertal Resort"><strong>Neuhaus Zillertal Resort - 4 Stars</strong></a></p>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img style="width: 260px; height: 141px;" src="/media/13090560/hotel-neuhaus-mayrhofen-260x141.jpg?width=260&amp;height=141" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/421e2943c3e54765b77f2efb8a8cb6f2" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen"><strong>Mayrhofen, Austria</strong></a></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This family-friendly hotel overlooks the Ziller Mountains, with extended valley views from the beautiful gardens. This hotel has lots to keep the whole family entertained including a heated outdoor pool, indoor pool and spa area. Children will also love the outdoor playground, in-house bowling alley, table tennis and billiard table.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/59460c7100664880a3f93ff191d15e13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59460c7100664880a3f93ff191d15e13}" title="Hotel Schweizerhof"><strong>Hotel Schweizerhof- 4.5 Stars</strong></a></p>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img style="width: 260px; height: 141px;" src="/media/13090561/hotel-schweizerhof-saas-fee-260x141.jpg?width=260&amp;height=141" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/49b3f802924945688833fc290f1c287a" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e}" title="Saas Fee"><strong>Saas Fee, Switzerland</strong></a></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This hotel is known for its fantastic facilities, attractive public areas and superb spa area. The ‘Wave’ spa offers the perfect retreat after a day of exploring and includes an indoor pool, as well as an outdoor whirlpool, steam room and sauna.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/29edcd3c50e4458281799c0617b52ba5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/29edcd3c50e4458281799c0617b52ba5}?departureDate=15%2F06%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Hotel La Folie Douce" data-anchor="?departureDate=15%2F06%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000">Hotel La Folie Douce - 3 Stars</a></strong></p>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img style="width: 260px; height: 141px;" src="/media/13090563/la-folie-douce-hotel-chamonix-piscine-260x141.jpg?width=260&amp;height=141" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/b3ef4cf251ee41be829759317664c116" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix"><strong>Chamonix, France</strong></a></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The hotel is the ideal choice for families. Its central location means it's easy to take advantage of all the activities available in Chamonix. There’s also lots to do in the hotel itself! Children will love swimming in the heated outdoor pool and for parents looking for some downtime, there is a free Kids Club for 4-12 year olds during school holidays.</span></p>
<div class="g4"></div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Self drive family holidays </h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Don’t fancy flying? <strong>Save up to £100 per person</strong> on a self drive family holiday and turn your European getaway into a summer road trip!  No luggage restrictions, no extra charges, just lots of fun family time exploring our family activity destinations.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Booking couldn’t be easier. Simply make sure the ‘self-drive’ option is checked upon booking your accommodation online. Or if you prefer, you can call our Reservations Team on </span><strong>01483 79 11 11</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Book your Inghams family holiday for the ultimate summer adventure</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands"></a><a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands"><img src="/media/13090673/in-safe-hands-flexibility-838x330-may-22.jpg" alt="In Safe Hands Inghams" data-udi="umb://media/46fe0fd3483443e6ae1e1a418008a220" /></a><a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands"></a></p>]]></bodyText>
